author: Josh Barro
title: Job Cuts Will Hit Industries You Don’t Expect
description: Job loss across the economy, even in sectors where you may not have known to look for it, will lead to less spending power and its ripple effects.
content: One observation that didnt make it into my Friday story on the bad-and-getting-worse employment picture is that job losses due to the coronavirus crisis are going to hit industries you dont expect. For example, health care: You might think thats a sector that… [+3065 chars]
